source_code_description: Hospital delay (for administrative or clinical reasons e.g. arranging appropriate facilities,for test to be carried out,specialist equipment,etc.)
Emergency - Home Accident (includes Accidental Poisoning in the home)
Routine elective (i.e. from waiting list as planned,excludes planned transfers)
Patient admitted on same day or following day as Attendance at Outpatients,not for medical reasons,but because suitable resources are available
Emergency - Deliberate Self Injury or Poisoning
Emergency - Other Injury (includes Accidental Poisoning other than in the home)
Patient Injury - Home Accident (including Accidental Poisoning in the home)
Patient Injury - Other Injury (including Accidental Poisoning other than in the home) - not elsewhere classified
Patient Injury - Self Inflicted (Injury or Poisoning)
Patient delay (for domestic,legal or other practical reasons)
